This is for new files added and changes to code.
New file added. Glide-distance-estimator-C.cpp
It is a C++ file mostly in C.
It may or may not work on all compilers.
November 2 2024.
Glide distance estimator2.cpp was added.
It puts user input in a while loop and uses
.find() and does not require a std::out_of_range
exception.
Becouse the code is more complicated the original
was left.
November 3 2024.
Glide distance estimator2.cpp had a while loop added to
altitude. A valid altitude must be entered to continue.
All C++ files have been formatted for easier reading.
December 29 2024.
A all C version has been added Glide distiance estimator.c.
It uses 2 array instead of a map for key value pairs.
Its simple but should not be used to store to many aircraft and glide ratios.
September 16 2025.
The convert string to int in Glide distance estimator.c has been changed from atoi to strtol.
this gives better error checking.
December 14 2025.
Error checking for fgets has been added to Glide distance estimator C.cpp.
A function to flush input buffer has bee added to Glide distance estimator C.cpp.
